> Hmm, should we not flush after clearing the dirty bit? That is, why does
> ptep_clear_flush_dirty() need a flush after clearing that bit? does it
> leak through in the tlb copy?
afaics you need to 
1) clear
2) flush 
3) check and go to 1) if needed
to be race free. 
